sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Owner as Site Owner
    participant FS as Formspree Dashboard
    participant Email as Email Provider
    participant Visitor as Site Visitor
    participant Site as Contact Page

    Note over Owner,Site: Change Contact Form Recipient

    Owner->>FS: Login to formspree.io
    Owner->>FS: Navigate to Account > Linked Emails
    Owner->>FS: Add new email address

    FS->>Email: Send verification email
    Email-->>Owner: Verification link
    Owner->>FS: Click verification link
    FS->>FS: Mark email as verified

    Owner->>FS: Navigate to Forms > Contact Form
    Owner->>FS: Click Workflow tab
    Owner->>FS: Scroll to Actions section
    Owner->>FS: Click 3-dot menu on Email row
    Owner->>FS: Select new recipient
    Owner->>FS: Save

    Note over Owner,Site: Test the Change

    Owner->>Site: Submit test message
    Site->>FS: POST form data
    FS->>Email: Deliver to new recipient
    Email-->>Owner: Test message received

    Note over Owner,Site: No site rebuild required - takes effect immediately
